metadata.name: TOK #1
metadata.description: The Skull is a representation of death serving as a Memento Mori, a reminder of the transience of life. We can also say that to experience a divine state one must go through an ego-death experience, momentarily letting go of reason, self-reflection and judgement. Being absorb within the moment. This is the second rarest.
